Version 0.7 (2025-08-27):
- More fixes for RHEL 9 and Lua 5.4 compatibility.

Version 0.6 (2025-03-07):
- Tag latest release for Lua 5.4 compatibility.

Version 0.5 (2013-12-20):
- Updates mostly for public release.

Version 0.4 (2012-10-03):
- Fix bug in hostlist find when prefix of hostname partially matches
  a prefix in the hostlist (e.g. hostlist --find=foo2 foo1-p2).

Version 0.3 (2012-02-16):
- Fix permissions on installed /usr/bin/hostlist.

Version 0.2 (2011-11-10):
- Fix bug in hostlist.union() that dropped final argument.
- Update to latest hostlist C code.
- Add hostlist -S, --sort

Version 0.1 (2010-01-25):
- Initial release
